		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64374182" name="comment_link_64374182" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23282014&amp;cid=64374182" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64374182)" >Commercial space was a new endeavor</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64374182" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64374182); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Informative)</span></h4>
