			<h4><a id="comment_link_64374238" name="comment_link_64374238" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23282014&amp;cid=64374238" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64374238)" >Musk should thank his lucky stars for this</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64374238" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64374238); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
